    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收到来自 “沃斯托克 ”综合研究站的求救信号后，“米尔尼 ”站的一名勇敢的极地探险家赶往救援。但是，南极基地紧锁的大门背后究竟隐藏着什么？通讯为何中断，所有员工又去了哪里？黑冰》的主人公必须解开重重谜团，面对危险的对手，并保持理智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/b91bbb5a2900b51ad2d87d111f14af14.poster.avif?t=1769963955\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/b91bbb5a2900b51ad2d87d111f14af14.webm?t=1769963955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/b91bbb5a2900b51ad2d87d111f14af14.mp4?t=1769963955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的名字来源于一种罕见的地质现象，这种现象是在南极冰层深处的极端条件下发生的。这种冰呈现不寻常的黑色，可能是由于其结构中存在来源不明的外来颗粒，可能是宇宙颗粒。例如，其成分中可能含有陨石尘埃或其他外来物质的痕迹，这些物质在数百万年前来到地球，并被冰川块掩埋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/19559050d5073a775860820d58ed5692.poster.avif?t=1769963955\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/19559050d5073a775860820d58ed5692.webm?t=1769963955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254050/extras/19559050d5073a775860820d58ed5692.mp4?t=1769963955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >压抑的孤独氛围</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满谜团和神秘感的建筑群</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弹药有限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间是你的主要对手</p></li></ul>",
